<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM6.6.6">
<l>taṉṉālē taṉṉuruvam payanta tāṉāyt tayaṅkoḷicēr mūvulakun tāṉāy vāṉāy</l>
<l>taṉṉālē tāṉuruvil mūrtti mūṉṟāyt tāṉāya ṉāyiṉāṉ caraṇeṉ ṟuyvīr</l>
<l>miṉṉāṭu vēlēntu viḷantai vēḷai viṇṇēṟat taṉivēluyt tulaka māṇṭa</l>
<l>teṉṉāṭaṉ kuṭakoṅkaṉ cōḻaṉ cērnta tirunaṟaiyūr maṇimāṭañ cērmiṉ kaḷē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>You who would be saved, naming as a refuge the one who became a herder,</l>
<l rend="indent">having become himself which his own body created by his own [will],</l>
<l>Having become the three worlds with glittering light,</l>
<l rend="indent">having become the heavens and, by his own [will],</l>
<l rend="indent">having become the three forms [which were] in his own body,</l>
<l>Gather at the beautiful raised shrine in Tirunaṟaiyūr where came the Cōḻa,</l>
<l rend="indent">the one of Konku in the West, the lord of the South</l>
<l>Who rules the world, sending a unique spear against the hero  of Viḷante</l>
<l rend="indent">so that [he] ascended to heaven, bearing a spear where lightning danced.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
